map <F11> :set nopaste<CR>
imap <F10> <C-O>:set paste<CR>
imap <F11> <nop>
set pastetoggle=<F11>
" open definition (using ctags) in new tab
nnoremap <silent><F12> <C-w><C-]><C-w>T

" aliases to prevent typos in close commands
